Put your receipts in this box. On closing you will receive the corresponding item for each of them.

Mind that these receipts are no longer being given out by the Deposit box and retrieval is done by the employee. This is just a legacy thing to deal with traded receipts still floating around.
Put one item in this box. It will be stored on your Morgan & Sons account when you close the box.

--------------------------------------------------------
Storing Items
--------------------------------------------------------
Put your item in the deposit box. On closing it will be stored as long as you have less than 20 items on your Morgan & Sons account and the item is not a plot item, gold, or a bag/box. You can store one item at a time. The box will be locked for 5 seconds after closing the lid.

Don't forget to take any remaining items out of the box!

--------------------------------------------------------
Retrieving Items
--------------------------------------------------------
You can browse yoru Morgan & Sons account by talking to the employee. You will be charged a fee of 5 gold pieces. Any receipts given out by the previous incarnation of the banking system will have to be processed by the Retrieve Box.

--------------------------------------------------------
Upgrading your account
--------------------------------------------------------
You can store up to 20 items with a single character. You can upgrade your account by talking to the employee:

Gold Member: 30 items, costs you 10.000 gold.
Platinum Member: 40 items, costs you 100.000 gold
Insane Member: 50 items, costs you 1.000.000 gold
